{
  "abilities": "擅长领域：文学、网球、羽毛球、电吉他、Steam游戏\n\n不擅长的事：数学、手工活、做饭（黑暗料理）\n\n日常消遣：坐在学校的大银杏树下看云、看展览、电影",
  "character_name": "林路",
  "character_schedule": {
    "day": 7
  },
  "comments": [],
  "completed": false,
  "dialogue": [
    {
      "content": "在干嘛啊，林老师",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "12:35",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "今天都没来找我",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "12:35"
    },
    {
      "content": "去体育馆打球了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "12:35"
    },
    {
      "content": "我想你周末肯定要睡到下午吧，就没发你",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "12:36"
    },
    {
      "content": "哈哈没错",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "12:36"
    },
    {
      "content": "刚醒",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "12:36"
    },
    {
      "content": "你打球打什么球啊？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "12:37"
    },
    {
      "content": "打网球",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "12:37"
    },
    {
      "content": "哇塞",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "12:37"
    },
    {
      "content": "这运动也太中产了吧",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "12:38"
    },
    {
      "content": "可别这么说",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "12:38"
    },
    {
      "content": "只是中二时期迷恋上了网球王子罢了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "12:38"
    },
    {
      "content": "你居然看过网球王子吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "12:39"
    },
    {
      "content": "这不纯纯少女漫吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "12:39"
    },
    {
      "content": "我小时候是当体育竞技看的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "12:39"
    },
    {
      "content": "谁也不知道后来会变成杀人网球这么离谱",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "12:40"
    },
    {
      "content": "【晕倒了】",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "12:40"
    },
    {
      "content": "我们那时候全班男生都一起在看啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "12:40"
    },
    {
      "content": "体育课的时候模仿小碎步",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "12:41"
    },
    {
      "content": "而且我们第一次接触网球王子，看的是真人版",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "12:41"
    },
    {
      "content": "hhhhhhh",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "12:41"
    },
    {
      "content": "真人版你也看得下去？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "12:42"
    },
    {
      "content": "不觉得羞耻吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "12:42"
    },
    {
      "content": "那时候我才三年级，四年级",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "12:42"
    },
    {
      "content": "正是对羞耻耐受度最高的时候",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "12:43"
    },
    {
      "content": "一点都不会觉得尴尬",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "12:43"
    },
    {
      "content": "只觉得龙马太帅了，太拽了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "12:43"
    },
    {
      "content": "hhh我们少爷就是很拽啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "12:44"
    },
    {
      "content": "我小时候的梦中情",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "12:44"
    },
    {
      "content": "我人生的初恋",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "12:44"
    },
    {
      "content": "hhh龙马少爷",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "12:45"
    },
    {
      "content": "久违的称呼",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "12:45"
    },
    {
      "content": "不过你的二次元初恋居然是龙马？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "12:45"
    },
    {
      "content": "对你而言，这部有点老了吧",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "12:46"
    },
    {
      "content": "还好",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "12:46"
    },
    {
      "content": "那时候我刚一年级吧，我的表姐很爱看。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "12:46"
    },
    {
      "content": "每个周末都拉着我一起看",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "12:47"
    },
    {
      "content": "嘿嘿，托他的福，我才可以上网",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "12:47"
    },
    {
      "content": "你表姐喜欢龙马，所以影响了你吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "12:47"
    },
    {
      "content": "我表姐最喜欢的是周助",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "12:48"
    },
    {
      "content": "腹黑眯眯眼",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "12:48"
    },
    {
      "content": "hhhh",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "12:48"
    },
    {
      "content": "死去的回忆开始攻击我",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "12:49"
    },
    {
      "content": "其实我觉得真人版的周助还可以...",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "12:49"
    },
    {
      "content": "打观月那一集真的有帅到我",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "12:49"
    },
    {
      "content": "我承认周柱确实挺帅的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "12:50"
    },
    {
      "content": "但我小时候很难get这种腹黑的魅力",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "12:50"
    },
    {
      "content": "龙马那种拽拽的，酷酷的才吸引我",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "12:50"
    },
    {
      "content": "hhh我从小就觉得龙马太装了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "12:51"
    },
    {
      "content": "他对小樱的态度太糟糕了，看的我火很大",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "12:51"
    },
    {
      "content": "对！",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "12:51"
    },
    {
      "content": "我小时候还讨厌小樱呢，觉得她老是缠着龙马影响他们打球",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "12:52"
    },
    {
      "content": "长大了我才知道其实是嫉妒，对女角色恶意太大了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "12:52"
    },
    {
      "content": "嗯，像这种全男主的竞技番",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "12:52"
    },
    {
      "content": "女主都承受了好大的恶意",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "12:53"
    },
    {
      "content": "当时我们班上有很多人不喜欢小樱，觉得他扭扭捏捏，一句话都说不清楚",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "12:53"
    },
    {
      "content": "但我一直都觉得小英没做错什么，害羞又没有伤害到其他人",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "12:53"
    },
    {
      "content": "而且她有自己的特长画画，也从来不去麻烦谁",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "12:54"
    },
    {
      "content": "对",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "12:54"
    },
    {
      "content": "小樱其实很好",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "12:54"
    },
    {
      "content": "要是在少女漫里，她就是人人爱的女主角了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "12:55"
    },
    {
      "content": "我想起来我们小时候看的动画女主角都太难了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "12:55"
    },
    {
      "content": "还有火影忍者的小樱",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "12:55"
    },
    {
      "content": "笑死，突然发现两个小樱都喜欢装装的死傲娇",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "12:56"
    },
    {
      "content": "火影你也看啊？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "12:56"
    },
    {
      "content": "我也火影迷",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "12:56"
    },
    {
      "content": "佐助是我的第二初恋",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "12:57"
    },
    {
      "content": "hhhh其实你才是小樱",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "12:57"
    },
    {
      "content": "我小时候真的也很讨厌小英，觉得她只会拖后腿",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "12:57"
    },
    {
      "content": "遇到一点事情就哭唧唧的，对鸣人态度还很恶劣",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "12:58"
    },
    {
      "content": "除了长得漂亮，一无是处，真不知道鸣人喜欢她什么",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "12:58"
    },
    {
      "content": "换个角度想，在鸣人和佐助这两个怪物天才之间",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "12:58"
    },
    {
      "content": "小樱能坚持下来，心态就已经很牛了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "12:59"
    },
    {
      "content": "她要是真的脆弱整天看着这两个人像怪物一样进步，早就崩溃了，不玩了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "12:59"
    },
    {
      "content": "是啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "12:59"
    },
    {
      "content": "，这也是我长大之后重刷才发现的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "13:00"
    },
    {
      "content": "小时候哪想得到那么多啊？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "13:00"
    },
    {
      "content": "你能想到那么多吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "13:00"
    },
    {
      "content": "好吧我也不能",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:01"
    },
    {
      "content": "我小时候虽然不讨厌小樱，但是只把她当挂件",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:01"
    },
    {
      "content": "觉得他没什么存在感，只起到一个花瓶的作用",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:01"
    },
    {
      "content": "火影的女角色里，我小时候比较喜欢井野",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:02"
    },
    {
      "content": "对，我小时候也更喜欢井野",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "13:02"
    },
    {
      "content": "我觉得她很酷很飒",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "13:02"
    },
    {
      "content": "因为井也野就是很酷很飒（什么废话",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:03"
    },
    {
      "content": "猪鹿蝶三个人的友谊，很纯粹",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:03"
    },
    {
      "content": "我从小就觉得他们的友谊和佐助，鸣人，小樱的不一样",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:03"
    },
    {
      "content": "都是三人小队,猪鹿蝶的友谊梗纯粹",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:04"
    },
    {
      "content": "hhh对",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "13:04"
    },
    {
      "content": "小时候经常担心鹿丸和井野在一起",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "13:04"
    },
    {
      "content": "hhhh那万万不能够啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:05"
    },
    {
      "content": "好朋友就是好朋友，要当一辈子的好朋友",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:05"
    },
    {
      "content": "但他最后和手鞠结婚了，我也很意外。八竿子打不着关系的人居然能凑成cp",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:05"
    },
    {
      "content": "那鸣雏佐樱结婚了怎么说",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "13:06"
    },
    {
      "content": "只能说是日本人也爱包寿司",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:06"
    },
    {
      "content": " 佐助配不上小樱。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:06"
    },
    {
      "content": "也不能说是配不上，就是前五六百集，他们俩没有任何相爱的迹象",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:07"
    },
    {
      "content": "佐助不愿意为小樱付出任何，他俩居然在一块了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:07"
    },
    {
      "content": "还不如小樱，少女时代的暗恋无疾而终了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:07"
    },
    {
      "content": "那你觉得小樱跟鸣人在一起好吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "13:08"
    },
    {
      "content": "那把雏田放在哪里？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:08"
    },
    {
      "content": "雏田和鸣人相互珍惜，相互欣赏啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:08"
    },
    {
      "content": "雏田是世上第一个没有发现名人任何天赋只因名人的话语行为，就相信他可以做到的人",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:09"
    },
    {
      "content": "名人也是。他以为他自己暗恋小樱的时候，哦，不是明恋。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:09"
    },
    {
      "content": "他也发现了默默努力坚持的雏田的可贵",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:09"
    },
    {
      "content": "他俩是最好的少年伙伴，最好的夫妻。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:10"
    },
    {
      "content": "【祝福】",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:10"
    },
    {
      "content": "可我是佐鸣党",
