      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "13:11"
    },
    {
      "content": "在下无法应对",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:11"
    },
    {
      "content": "在那个还没有弹幕区，只有评论区的年代",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:11"
    },
    {
      "content": "佐鸣党和雏鸣党就能吵几百楼了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:12"
    },
    {
      "content": "虽然我觉得佐助和鸣人只是纯粹的兄弟情，很深很深的羁绊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:12"
    },
    {
      "content": "他们之间的友谊和羁绊，不亚于任何一场伟大的爱情",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:12"
    },
    {
      "content": "但是有的人认为爱情更伟大，非要往爱情上磕，那我也没招",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:13"
    },
    {
      "content": "确实太复杂了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:13"
    },
    {
      "content": "hhhh",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "13:13"
    },
    {
      "content": "因为我觉得鸣人和佐助之间更有张力",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "13:14"
    },
    {
      "content": "还有600多集，就是在讲他们的故事啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "13:14"
    },
    {
      "content": "绕着他们俩之间的羁绊展开，要是他们俩没有击败，就没有火影者了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "13:14"
    },
    {
      "content": "所以最后看到佐樱结婚，我真的气死了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "13:15"
    },
    {
      "content": "我到了后来已经觉得小樱很好了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "13:15"
    },
    {
      "content": "但佐助真的不是一个适合结婚的对象，我觉得这个世界上除了名人，没有人会受得了他我",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "13:15"
    },
    {
      "content": "佐助可以不结婚",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:16"
    },
    {
      "content": "我也觉得佐助不应该结婚",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:16"
    },
    {
      "content": "他就是匹孤狼",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:16"
    },
    {
      "content": "我他可以偶尔跟好兄弟们一起切磋忍术， 打打闹闹",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:17"
    },
    {
      "content": " 但他绝不适合成为一个丈夫，放在家庭里面",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:17"
    },
    {
      "content": "佐助这样的性格太消耗小樱的热情了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:17"
    },
    {
      "content": "对，可惜了我们家春野樱",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "13:18"
    },
    {
      "content": "啊，忍不住感叹一句，好复古啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:18"
    },
    {
      "content": " 好多年没跟人聊火影了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:18"
    },
    {
      "content": "梦回初中时代",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:19"
    },
    {
      "content": "hhhh",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "13:19"
    },
    {
      "content": "我也是",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "13:19"
    },
    {
      "content": "现在大家看到最新的战斗番是咒术回战吧",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "13:20"
    },
    {
      "content": "...",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:20"
    },
    {
      "content": "【多么痛的领悟】",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:20"
    },
    {
      "content": "无论如何也躲不过咒术回战吗？只要聊热血番就一定会说到",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:21"
    },
    {
      "content": "条悟死了之后我就再也不看了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:21"
    },
    {
      "content": "我也...",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "13:21"
    },
    {
      "content": "那我期待一个秽土转生",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "13:22"
    },
    {
      "content": "别期待了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:22"
    },
    {
      "content": "我悲观消极，我觉得制作组只会变着花样折磨我们",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:22"
    },
    {
      "content": "你就这么说弃就弃了?",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "13:23"
    },
    {
      "content": "嗯",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:23"
    },
    {
      "content": "毕竟咒术回战不是从小追的，没有革命感情",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:23"
    },
    {
      "content": "好羡慕你的洒脱",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "13:24"
    },
    {
      "content": "说放下也放下，你在感情中也是一个这么无情的人吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "13:24"
    },
    {
      "content": "话题到底是怎么转到这里的？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:24"
    },
    {
      "content": "你不觉得生硬吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:25"
    },
    {
      "content": "[惊呆了]",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:25"
    },
    {
      "content": "不会啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "13:25"
    },
    {
      "content": "你是不是心虚不敢回答？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "13:26"
    },
    {
      "content": "我心虚什么？我都没谈过恋爱",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:26"
    },
    {
      "content": "我的放下，只针对一些小事吧。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:26"
    },
    {
      "content": "大事上我放不下的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:27"
    },
    {
      "content": "潇洒是我装的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:27"
    },
    {
      "content": "【两副面孔】",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:27"
    },
    {
      "content": "比如说呢？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "13:28"
    },
    {
      "content": "我们普通人能有什么大事啊？买车买房？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "13:28"
    },
    {
      "content": "要不要结婚，生孩子，跳槽？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "13:28"
    },
    {
      "content": "你还记得我之前和你说我在泰国教书吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:29"
    },
    {
      "content": "嗯你还跟我说很多泰国离谱的八卦呢",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "13:29"
    },
    {
      "content": "我在泰国教书的时候，有一个学生",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:29"
    },
    {
      "content": "他的父亲去缅北诈骗了，究竟是被骗还是自愿？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:30"
    },
    {
      "content": "无法证实，因为他的父亲杳无音讯",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:30"
    },
    {
      "content": "后来他妈妈也生了病，他只好辍学去打工",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:30"
    },
    {
      "content": "他有个妹妹，那时才八岁，经常来学校等他放学回家",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:31"
    },
    {
      "content": "现在她的妹妹在读初中，我正在资助她，希望她能够完成学业",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:31"
    },
    {
      "content": "泰国那个地方真是乱",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "13:31"
    },
    {
      "content": "话说你怎么想到去资助她？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "13:32"
    },
    {
      "content": "做人还得靠自救",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:32"
    },
    {
      "content": "因为他的妹妹，哎呀，好绕口啊，直接和你说名字吧",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:32"
    },
    {
      "content": "他的妹妹叫阿南雅，阿南雅很喜欢读书，可他们的家庭条件无法支持两个人读书",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:33"
    },
    {
      "content": "阿南雅会在课堂外面偷偷听课",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:33"
    },
    {
      "content": "她还给我送过鸡蛋，希望能跟我交换一本语文书",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:33"
    },
    {
      "content": "或许他不懂读书能改变命运，但他知道这是他那时候唯一能做的事",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:34"
    },
    {
      "content": "像他们那边女孩子如果没有家庭支持他们读书，找到一个好工作可能就会早早嫁人",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:34"
    },
    {
      "content": "要是运气再差一点，遇到一个不靠谱的丈夫，把他们卖去红灯区",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:34"
    },
    {
      "content": "这一生就再没有机会了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:35"
    },
    {
      "content": "阿南亚的坚持打动了我，我想尽自己所能的帮一下她",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:35"
    },
    {
      "content": "啊？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "13:35"
    },
    {
      "content": "你原来人那么好吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "13:36"
    },
    {
      "content": "你身上居然还有那么戏剧的故事",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "13:36"
    },
    {
      "content": "但是话又说回来，你资助了他读书之后，他哥为什么还要去打工啊？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "13:36"
    },
    {
      "content": "一个14岁的少年，生长在那样的国家",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:37"
    },
    {
      "content": "又有下落不明的爸爸，重病的妈妈",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:37"
    },
    {
      "content": "他没法把心思放在学校里了。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:37"
    },
    {
      "content": "我也试图劝过他，但他觉得打工才是他的出路，他的命运就是赚钱",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:38"
    },
    {
      "content": "打工哪能赚到钱啊？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "13:38"
    },
    {
      "content": "打工是那么好赚钱的吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "13:38"
    },
    {
      "content": "他还小，这些道理告诉他，他不会理解的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:39"
    },
    {
      "content": "这也算是他的坚强，他和命运抗衡的方式吧",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:39"
    },
    {
      "content": "因为无法改变，所以我选择支持他",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:39"
    },
    {
      "content": "偶尔他也会给我发一些他的消息",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:40"
    },
    {
      "content": "那他现在在做什么？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "13:40"
    },
    {
      "content": "是在做正途吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "13:40"
    },
    {
      "content": "嗯",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:41"
    },
    {
      "content": "他有初中文凭啊，在那边不算太差",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:41"
    },
    {
      "content": "他在一家印刷厂学习做设计,搞一些产品的包装，排版什么的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:41"
    },
    {
      "content": "上个月他发消息给我，说今年有转正做设计师的希望",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:42"
    },
    {
      "content": "真好啊！",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "13:42"
    },
    {
      "content": "希望他能够幸福吧",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "13:42"
    },
    {
      "content": "嗯",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:43"
    },
    {
      "content": "阿南雅的成绩也不错，现在在读初二",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:43"
    },
    {
      "content": "按照这个势头保持下去，应该能上大学",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:43"
    },
    {
      "content": "那上了大学你也会资助她吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "13:44"
    },
    {
      "content": "我和阿南雅的哥哥商量过，哥哥觉得他那个时候应该有足够的钱供阿南雅上大学了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:44"
    },
    {
      "content": "看到时候他们的情况吧，如果有需要，我可以继续资助",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:44"
    },
    {
      "content": "老师，你真是送佛送到西",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "13:45"
    },
    {
      "content": "大好人一个",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "13:45"
    },
    {
      "content": "略尽绵薄之力",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:45"
    },
    {
      "content": "在泰国那段时间，我接触到的不幸的学生真是太多了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:46"
    },
    {
      "content": "我也只帮了那么一个",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:46"
    },
    {
      "content": "果然，人还是得靠自救",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "13:46"
    },
    {
      "content": "你说他以后会回报你吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "13:47"
    },
    {
      "content": "他们兄妹俩经常这么说",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:47"
    },
    {
      "content": "我是觉得并不重要",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:47"
    },
    {
      "content": "不过我也会对他们讲，我很期待他们的回报，我相信他们以后会把日子过好的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:48"
    },
    {
      "content": "这样会给他们压力吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "13:48"
    },
    {
      "content": "恰恰相反，相信是他们的动力",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:48"
    },
    {
      "content": "我更宁愿他把我的资助认为一种投资，因为他们有潜力，有可能有希望我才投资",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:49"
    },
    {
      "content": "所以我们之间关系是平等的，不是施舍",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:49"
    },
    {
      "content": "你这个就叫做那个什么什么主义来着文什么？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "13:49"
    },
    {
      "content": "人文主义关怀",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:50"
    },
    {
      "content": "对对对，就是这个意思",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "13:50"
    },
    {
      "content": "以前语文老师教过达则兼济天下",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "13:50"
    },
    {
      "content": "你真的是圣父啊，这次不是嘲讽你的意思",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "13:51"
    },
    {
      "content": "hhhh",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "13:51"
    },
    {
