      "timestamp": "15:55"
    },
    {
      "content": "有种诡异的辉煌",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "15:56"
    },
    {
      "content": "旧神已死，新神当立",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "15:56"
    },
    {
      "content": "对对对对！！！",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "15:56"
    },
    {
      "content": "不愧是教文学的，说话就是好听",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "15:57"
    },
    {
      "content": "我也想表达出这种感觉，但我说不出来，词汇好匮乏",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "15:57"
    },
    {
      "content": "没关系，让会的表达的人去表达就可以了啊？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "15:57"
    },
    {
      "content": "我学语文就是为了让我的表达更加的准确，更加的有美感",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "15:58"
    },
    {
      "content": "你能够get到我很开心。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "15:58"
    },
    {
      "content": "老师，我要怎么样才能像你一样说话好听啊？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "15:58"
    },
    {
      "content": "阅读，除此之外，别无捷径",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "15:59"
    },
    {
      "content": "就没有那种速成的书吗？",
