    },
    {
      "content": "嗯我要是认同了这种方式，不去揭穿。那就是默许她们用路径依赖来给我制造麻烦",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "17:16"
    },
    {
      "content": "【绝不ok】",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "17:16"
    },
    {
      "content": "你还挺清醒",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "17:17"
    },
    {
      "content": "主要是我不想当个弱智",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "17:17"
    },
    {
      "content": "我觉得揣着明白装糊涂，被绿茶蒙蔽的男的很弱智",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "17:17"
    },
    {
      "content": "好骂",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "17:18"
    },
    {
      "content": "我要是像你一样会骂人就好了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "17:18"
    },
    {
      "content": "我们不支持使用脏字哦",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "17:18"
    },
    {
      "content": "我觉得骂人的最高境界就是戳到痛处，但又没有一句脏话",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "17:19"
    },
    {
      "content": "我愿将之称其为刻薄",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "17:19"
    },
    {
      "content": "hhh适当的刻薄，无伤大雅",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "17:19"
    },
    {
      "content": "我喜欢的很多文学大师都挺刻薄的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "17:20"
    },
    {
      "content": "最经典的就是钱钟书",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "17:20"
    },
    {
      "content": "hhhh",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "17:20"
    },
    {
      "content": "我好像听过他一句名句，对丑人怎么那个什么来着？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "17:21"
    },
    {
      "content": "对丑人细看是种残忍",
